  "events": [
    {
      "at_ms": 0,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 1,
      "speaker": "黒田",
      "text": "とりあえずQ3時点でARRは想定より伸びてます。\nただCACが若干悪化してるので、LTVとのバランス見ないと危ないです。",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "ARR",
        "CAC",
        "LTV"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 450,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "ARR",
        "CAC",
        "LTV"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 2200,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 2,
      "speaker": "石井",
      "text": "広告CPAかなり上がってますよね。\n特にSMB向け獲得。",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "SMB"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 2650,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "SMB"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 4400,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 3,
      "speaker": "長谷川",
      "text": "その代わりチャーン率は改善してます。\nオンボーディング施策かなり効いてる。",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "チャーン率"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 4850,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "チャーン率"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 6600,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 4,
      "speaker": "黒田",
      "text": "NRRどうでしたっけ？",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "NRR"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 7050,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "NRR"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 8800,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 5,
      "speaker": "石井",
      "text": "現状112%です。\nただEnterprise側がかなり牽引してるので、Mid-market単体で見るとそこまで強くないです。",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "Enterprise"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 9250,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "Enterprise"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 11000,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 6,
      "speaker": "高田",
      "text": "Burn Rateはまだ許容範囲？",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "Burn Rate"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 11450,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "Burn Rate"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 13200,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 7,
      "speaker": "石井",
      "text": "現状Runway的には18ヶ月。\nただAI推論コスト想定以上です。",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "Runway"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 13650,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "Runway"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 15400,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 8,
      "speaker": "黒田",
      "text": "Azure OpenAI側？",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "Azure OpenAI"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 15850,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "Azure OpenAI"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 17600,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 9,
      "speaker": "石井",
      "text": "はい。\nInference costが結構重いです。\nRAGの再検索頻度が高くて。",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "Inference cost",
        "RAG"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 18050,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "Inference cost",
        "RAG"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 19800,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 10,
      "speaker": "長谷川",
      "text": "でもあそこ削るとUX落ちません？",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 22000,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 11,
      "speaker": "黒田",
      "text": "いや、Retention落ちる方がまずい。\n今一番重要なの継続率なので。",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "Retention"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 22450,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "Retention"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 24200,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 12,
      "speaker": "高田",
      "text": "ところでFabric連携っていつGA予定なんでしたっけ？",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "Fabric",
        "GA"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 24650,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "Fabric",
        "GA"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 26400,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 13,
      "speaker": "石井",
      "text": "たしかFY26 H2想定だったと思います。\nまだPreviewです。",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "Preview"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 26850,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "Preview"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 28600,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 14,
      "speaker": "黒田",
      "text": "そこGAしないと大手導入止まりませんよね。",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "GA"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 29050,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "GA"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 30800,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 15,
      "speaker": "長谷川",
      "text": "特に金融系。\nガバナンス周りかなり厳しいので。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 33000,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 16,
      "speaker": "石井",
      "text": "あとEntra ID連携必須って言われるケース増えてます。",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "Entra ID"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 33450,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "Entra ID"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 35200,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 17,
      "speaker": "高田",
      "text": "SSOなしだと通らない？",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "SSO"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 35650,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "SSO"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 37400,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 18,
      "speaker": "石井",
      "text": "最近ほぼ無理ですね。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 39600,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 19,
      "speaker": "黒田",
      "text": "代理店経由案件どうなってます？",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 41800,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 20,
      "speaker": "長谷川",
      "text": "今月2件PoC入ってます。\nただ片方、Decision Makerまだ見えてないです。",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "PoC",
        "Decision Maker"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 42250,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "PoC",
        "Decision Maker"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 44000,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 21,
      "speaker": "石井",
      "text": "Championはいるんですけどね。",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "Champion"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 44450,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "Champion"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 46200,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 22,
      "speaker": "黒田",
      "text": "それ一番危ないやつだ…。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 48400,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 23,
      "speaker": "高田",
      "text": "ちなみに今期KPIって結局何優先なんでしたっけ？",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "KPI"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 48850,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "KPI"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 50600,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 24,
      "speaker": "黒田",
      "text": "MRRよりRetention。\n新規獲得競争かなりレッドオーシャン化してるので。",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "MRR",
        "Retention"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 51050,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "MRR",
        "Retention"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 52800,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 25,
      "speaker": "長谷川",
      "text": "とはいえPL的には新規売上も欲しいですよね。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 55000,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 26,
      "speaker": "高田",
      "text": "あー、Copilot文脈に乗せる感じか。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 57200,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 27,
      "speaker": "黒田",
      "text": "そう。\n単体AIツールだと差別化難しいので。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 59400,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 28,
      "speaker": "長谷川",
      "text": "あと最近「AI導入したいけど社員が使いこなせない」相談かなり増えてます。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 61600,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 29,
      "speaker": "石井",
      "text": "結局そこなんですよね。\nみんな知識ギャップで会議止まる。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 63800,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 30,
      "speaker": "高田",
      "text": "新人教育コストも減りそうですよね。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 66000,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 31,
      "speaker": "長谷川",
      "text": "ただHR評価に見えると危ない気はします。",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "HR"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 66450,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "HR"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 68200,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 32,
      "speaker": "黒田",
      "text": "絶対「理解力スコア化」はやらない方がいい。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 70400,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 33,
      "speaker": "高田",
      "text": "炎上する未来しか見えない。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 72600,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 34,
      "speaker": "長谷川",
      "text": "あと多分ユーザー、知らないって認めたくないですよ。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 74800,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 35,
      "speaker": "石井",
      "text": "若干ふざけてる名前の方が心理障壁下がるかなと。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 77000,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 36,
      "speaker": "高田",
      "text": "たしかに「Knowledge Gap Optimizer」より押しやすい。",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "GA"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 77450,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "GA"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 79200,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 37,
      "speaker": "長谷川",
      "text": "逆に親しみある。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 81400,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 38,
      "speaker": "石井",
      "text": "略語だらけ会議ログ流します。\nADR、SKU、RAG、ARR、EBITDA全部入り。",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "ARR",
        "RAG"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 81850,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "ARR",
        "RAG"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 83600,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 39,
      "speaker": "高田",
      "text": "地獄みたいな会議だな…。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 85800,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 40,
      "speaker": "石井",
      "text": "その中で：\n「わからないけど聞けない」\nを再現します。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 88000,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 41,
      "speaker": "長谷川",
      "text": "かなりリアル。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 90200,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 42,
      "speaker": "黒田",
      "text": "で、クリックした単語だけ、\n後で個人向け補足生成される？",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 92400,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 43,
      "speaker": "石井",
      "text": "そうです。\n全体議事録じゃなくて、\n「自分が置いていかれた部分だけ」。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 94600,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 44,
      "speaker": "高田",
      "text": "それ結構面白いですね。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 96800,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 45,
      "speaker": "長谷川",
      "text": "会議後のキャッチアップかなり楽になりそう。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 99000,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 46,
      "speaker": "高田",
      "text": "賢明。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 101200,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 47,
      "speaker": "石井",
      "text": "Azure Functions + OpenAIだけでまず成立させます。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 103400,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 48,
      "speaker": "黒田",
      "text": "その方がいい。\n今回インフラ勝負じゃないので。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 105600,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 49,
      "speaker": "高田",
      "text": "AKSやり始めたら終わる。",
      "highlight_terms": [
        "AKS"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 106050,
      "type": "term_chip",
      "terms": [
        "AKS"
      ]
    },
    {
      "at_ms": 107800,
      "type": "line",
      "index": 50,
      "speaker": "石井",
      "text": "完全に同意です。",
      "highlight_terms": []
    }
  ]
}
